text: We have a slang term in the west, "simp". A simp is a guy who has a crush on a girl who has no interest in him at all - or something similar. The guy will give her money and gifts, do favors for her; anything, hoping she'll change her mind. That's "simping". We joke that we're simping for Gura, but because she's a shark, we call it "shrimping", as a pun.
